{"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.EqCnstr","instances":[],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Simp","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.Var","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.DvdCnstr","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.LeCnstr","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.ToInt","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.CommRing"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Cutsat/EqCnstr.lean#L525-L584","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.internalize","line":525,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Cutsat/EqCnstr.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.internalize","doc":"Internalizes an integer (and `Nat`) expression. Here are the different cases that are handled.\n\n- `a + b` when `parent?` is not `+`, `≤`, or `∣`\n- `k * a` when `k` is a numeral and `parent?` is not `+`, `*`, `≤`, `∣`\n- numerals when `parent?` is not `+`, `*`, `≤`, `∣`.\n  Recall that we must internalize numerals to make sure we can propagate equalities\n  back to the congruence closure module. Example: we have `f 5`, `f x`, `x - y = 3`, `y = 2`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Cutsat/EqCnstr.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.internalize\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Arith</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cutsat</span>.<span class=\"name\">internalize</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">parent?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Cutsat/EqCnstr.lean#L329-L340","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.processNewDiseqImpl","line":329,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Cutsat/EqCnstr.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.processNewDiseqImpl","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Cutsat/EqCnstr.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.processNewDiseqImpl\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Arith</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cutsat</span>.<span class=\"name\">processNewDiseqImpl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a </span><span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Cutsat/EqCnstr.lean#L273-L284","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.processNewEqImpl","line":273,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Cutsat/EqCnstr.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.Cutsat.processNewEqImpl","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Cutsat/EqCnstr.html#Lean.Meta.Gr